*** Update File: /var/home/atumia/caracal-stuff-latest/caracal-dev/caracal-software-installer/README.md
@@
 The UI is catalog-driven, so adding more packages later is mostly a matter of dropping in scripts and extending the metadata in `internal/catalog`.
+
+Download URLs and related upstream metadata now live in [data/download-index.csv](/var/home/atumia/caracal-stuff-latest/caracal-dev/caracal-software-installer/data/download-index.csv). The shell installers resolve their URLs from that index through [scripts/download-index.py](/var/home/atumia/caracal-stuff-latest/caracal-dev/caracal-software-installer/scripts/download-index.py), which keeps link updates spreadsheet-friendly.
+
+To validate the index locally:
+
+```bash
+python3 scripts/download-index.py validate
+python3 scripts/download-index.py validate --check-urls
+```
+
+The `--check-urls` mode is suitable for a daily cron job or CI check that reports broken upstream links.
